# NPM Workspace Usage

This project uses npm workspaces. Always run npm commands from the repository root using workspace flags.

## Installing Packages

```bash
# ✅ GOOD - Install from root with workspace flag
cd /home/anant/work/anant/projects/doc-workflow-project/al-demo
npm install <package-name> -w apps/web

# ❌ BAD - Don't cd into workspace and install
cd apps/web
npm install <package-name>
```

## Running Scripts

```bash
# ✅ GOOD - Run scripts from root
npm run dev --workspace=apps/web
npm run build --workspace=apps/web

# ❌ BAD - Don't cd into workspace
cd apps/web
npm run dev
```

## Workspace Structure

- Root: `/home/anant/work/anant/projects/doc-workflow-project/al-demo`
- Web app: `apps/web`
- API: `api` (Python, uses uv)
